351
11:00:00,000 --> 11:06:00,000
Fourth, you must have at least one rightsizing recommendation.
Run the rightsizing API query.

352
11:06:00,000 --> 11:12:00,000
You should see at least one deployment with currentCPU and recommendedCPU.
