354
11:18:00,000 --> 11:24:00,000
If you have all four, you're ready for Series four.

355
11:24:00,000 --> 11:30:00,000
In Series four, we deploy Karpenter.
Karpenter is Kubernetes-native autoscaling.

356
11:30:00,000 --> 11:36:00,000
It replaces the traditional Cluster Autoscaler.
It launches nodes in seconds instead of minutes.

357
11:36:00,000 --> 11:42:00,000
