from a list you provide.

358
11:42:00,000 --> 11:48:00,000
It consolidates workloads to reduce the number of nodes.
It can save you thirty to forty percent on compute costs.

359
11:48:00,000 --> 11:54:00,000
Where Kubecost shows you the waste,
Karpenter eliminates it automatically.

